data.description: Lockmar Estates home situated on a large .34 lot. New Roof 2021. New Septic 2022. New Electric Panel 2021. Large solar heated pool with screen enclosure. Patio  area & pool deck are just under 1000 sq ft in size.  Large fenced yard all around with 2 sheds on the property that convey. This home features a wood burning fireplace adding warmth and charm to this home. 2 Car Garage has been converted into livng space with central AC.  Split floorplan features 3 Bedrooms. 2 Updated full bathrooms, kitchen with nook area & large family room with fireplace.  Considered to be one of the best areas in Palm Bay, Lockmar Estates.  Perfect home for someone looking for piece of mind and privacy. Ample room to bring boats, rv and more. No HOA. No neighbors behind this home.
